CatDescriptText: El Cabana Club Casino was located at 6324 Station Street, East Liberty.
TitMainTitle: Group portrait of men, possibly including Harry Bobo seated third from left, and man on right wearing plaid shirt under jacket, and women, gathered around tables in El Cabana Club Casino with textured walls, angled florescent lights, sign on wall reading "Minimum charge $1 per person", and band with drums, bass, and saxophone performing in background
